spawns_inside_hazards.property_description:
Normally dangerous blocks that this entity can spawn inside.
This only includes wither roses, sweet berry bushes, and powder snow.
See Fire Immune for entities that can spawn inside of fire.

base_armor.property_description: The amount of armor points this has without wearing anything.

height_offset.property_description: The height offset this entity adds to itself when riding a vehicle.

hurt_by_water.property_description: Whether this is hurt by water, rain, and splash/lingering water bottles.

living.property_description: Whether this is a LivingEntity. Includes armor stands.

entries.Drowned: 20.0 and 40.0 - 100.0 (Spawns with 20.0 health due to MC-219981)

mounted_height_offset.property_description: The height offset this entity adds to its passengers.

saved_on_reload.property_description: Whether this is saved to the world. Entities that are not saved are lost when unloaded.
